00:06:04,905 --> 00:06:09,635
Between two and 20 neutrons and alphas,
which are helium nuclei,

109
00:06:09,635 --> 00:06:12,737
two protons, two neutrons,
it's about 20 also.

110
00:06:12,737 --> 00:06:17,575
