00:06:34,977 --> 00:06:37,475
is equal to 100 REM.

117
00:06:39,155 --> 00:06:42,441
On this table,
we have the physiological effect

118
00:06:42,441 --> 00:06:45,223
of radiation and typical doses.

119
00:06:45,223 --> 00:06:47,333
We try, you see, on top,

120
00:06:47,333 --> 00:06:54,121
we try to always stay
below 100 REM, or one Sievert,

121
00:06:54,121 --> 00:06:57,070
because this is
vomiting effective threshold.

122
00:06:57,070 --> 00:07:03,944
As long as you are in the area
between 5 and 10, maybe 20 REMs,

123
00:07:03,944 --> 00:07:05,472
you are okay.

124
00:07:05,472 --> 00:07:08,801
If you go toward 100,
