126
00:07:12,568 --> 00:07:15,520
then you have
significant medical problems.

127
00:07:16,180 --> 00:07:18,795
And you have,
in the lower part of this table,

128
00:07:18,795 --> 00:07:23,328
the effect for different situations
including a typical Shuttle mission,

129
00:07:23,328 --> 00:07:27,561
where you had normally,
a total or less than one REM.

130
00:07:28,101 --> 00:07:30,583
As long as you are on Low Earth Orbit,

131
00:07:30,583 --> 00:07:32,829
including the International Space Station,

132
00:07:32,829 --> 00:07:34,407
the radiation is not very, very high,

133
00:07:34,407 --> 00:07:38,345
because you are protected,
on one hand, by the magnetosphere,

134
00:07:38,345 --> 00:07:41,300
and by the atmosphere
that is remaining above you.

135
00:07:41,300 --> 00:07:44,006
Remember that at 400 kilometers altitude,

136
00:07:44,006 --> 00:07:47,076
this is the altitude of the orbit of
the International Space Station,

137
00:07:47,076 --> 00:07:48,675
you are in the ionosphere,

138
00:07:48,675 --> 00:07:51,343
you still have a portion
of the ionosphere above you,

139
00:07:51,343 --> 00:07:54,849
which causes an absorption
of the particles,

140
00:07:54,849 --> 00:07:57,683
whether they come from the Sun
or from the Galaxy.

